PROGRAM DESCRIPTIONS:
*******************************************************************************
bc 
Usage: 
    bc [inputfile] [output vtk] 
Description:
    Computes betweenness centrality (in progress)
*******************************************************************************
split 
  Usage: 
    split [input voxel file] [output voxel file]

    Fast code for dividing up a voxel data set into clusters of contiguous
    voxels, (i.e. voxels that share a face, but not an edge). 
*******************************************************************************
